---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Desarrollador Backend"
  description="Portfolio de Josep Company Cuesta, desarrollador backend especializado en SAP BTP, CAP y Node.js."
  image="/og-image.jpg"
>
  <section>
    <div class="main-container">
      <p class="route">~/sobre-mi</p>
      <h1>Josep Company Cuesta</h1>
      <h3>// desarrollador de software</h3>
      <br />
      <p>
        Soy desarrollador de software full-stack con más de 5 años de experiencia. Me
        gusta aprender nuevas tecnologías y trabajar en proyectos de distintos ámbitos,
        desde aplicaciones empresariales sobre <code>SAP BTP</code> hasta desarrollo web, integraciones
        con inteligencia artificial e IoT.<br /> Actualmente estoy especializado en el desarrollo
        de servicios backend con <code>Node.js</code> y <code>SAP CAP</code>
      </p>
      <br />
      <section>
        <h2>conectar<span style="color: var(--color-primary)">()</span></h2>
        <p>
          Si quieres contactar conmigo, puedes hacerlo a través de las redes sociales o
          enviarme un correo electrónico
        </p>

        <div class="social-icons">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/Pepecc"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="GitHub"
          >
            <svg
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="bottom-icons"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="25"
              height="25"
              fill="#000000"
              viewBox="0 0 256 256"
            >
              <path
                d="M208.31,75.68A59.78,59.78,0,0,0,202.93,28,8,8,0,0,0,196,24a59.75,59.75,0,0,0-48,24H124A59.75,59.75,0,0,0,76,24a8,8,0,0,0-6.93,4,59.78,59.78,0,0,0-5.38,47.68A58.14,58.14,0,0,0,56,104v8a56.06,56.06,0,0,0,48.44,55.47A39.8,39.8,0,0,0,96,192v8H72a24,24,0,0,1-24-24A40,40,0,0,0,8,136a8,8,0,0,0,0,16,24,24,0,0,1,24,24,40,40,0,0,0,40,40H96v16a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V192a24,24,0,0,1,48,0v40a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V192a39.8,39.8,0,0,0-8.44-24.53A56.06,56.06,0,0,0,216,112v-8A58.14,58.14,0,0,0,208.31,75.68ZM200,112a40,40,0,0,1-40,40H112a40,40,0,0,1-40-40v-8a41.74,41.74,0,0,1,6.9-22.48A8,8,0,0,0,80,73.83a43.81,43.81,0,0,1,.79-33.58,43.88,43.88,0,0,1,32.32,20.06A8,8,0,0,0,119.82,64h32.35a8,8,0,0,0,6.74-3.69,43.87,43.87,0,0,1,32.32-20.06A43.81,43.81,0,0,1,192,73.83a8.09,8.09,0,0,0,1,7.65A41.72,41.72,0,0,1,200,104Z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/josep-c-229b561b5/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="LinkedIn"
          >
            <svg
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="bottom-icons"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="25"
              height="25"
              fill="#000000"
              viewBox="0 0 256 256"
            >
              <path
                d="M216,24H40A16,16,0,0,0,24,40V216a16,16,0,0,0,16,16H216a16,16,0,0,0,16-16V40A16,16,0,0,0,216,24Zm0,192H40V40H216V216ZM96,112v64a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V112a8,8,0,0,1,16,0Zm88,28v36a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V140a20,20,0,0,0-40,0v36a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V112a8,8,0,0,1,15.79-1.78A36,36,0,0,1,184,140ZM100,84A12,12,0,1,1,88,72,12,12,0,0,1,100,84Z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:contacto@josepcompany.dev">
          contacto@josepcompany.dev
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>

    <style>
      .main-container {
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        max-width: 750px;
        min-height: 100vh;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        background-color: var(--color-surface);
        transition:
          background-color 0.3s,
          border-color 0.3s;
        color: var(--color-text);
      }

      .route {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .social-icons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .bottom-icons {
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      :global(html.dark) .bottom-icons {
        fill: var(--color-text);
      }

      :global(html.dark) .bottom-icons:hover {
        fill: var(--color-text-secondary);
      }

      .bottom-icons:hover {
        fill: var(--color-text-secondary);
      }

      .contact-link {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary) 45%, transparent);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
    </style>
  </section>
</Layout>
